body:
On nethermind node when executing this call on goerli:
```
curl -X "POST" "https://nethermind-goerli.alt.technology/" \
     -H 'Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8' \
     -d $'{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "eth_getProof",
  "id": 1,
  "params": [
    "0x85774329243acee1333ccae49be011a056f0e1b9",
    [
      "0x65a7ed542fb37fe237fdfbdd70b31598523fe5b32879e307bae27a0bd9581c08"
    ],
    "0x8d7e5171a770707bd7dab7386a659d2399b1404b9b3e49eb1658fc3cd51710ca"
  ]
}'
```

There is such response:
```
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "result": {
    ......
    "storageProof": [
      {
        ......
        **"value": "0x041337600e1179b05750a3490bd546ca1a0c5123"**
      }
    ]
  },
  "id": 1
}
```

Where on geth node:
```
curl -X "POST" "https://goerli.gateway.tenderly.co/" \
     -H 'Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8' \
     -d $'{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "eth_getProof",
  "id": 1,
  "params": [
    "0x85774329243acee1333ccae49be011a056f0e1b9",
    [
      "0x65a7ed542fb37fe237fdfbdd70b31598523fe5b32879e307bae27a0bd9581c08"
    ],
    "0x8d7e5171a770707bd7dab7386a659d2399b1404b9b3e49eb1658fc3cd51710ca"
  ]
}'
```

response looks like this:
```
{
  "id": 1,
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "result": {
    ......    
    "storageProof": [
      {
        ......
        **"value": "0x41337600e1179b05750a3490bd546ca1a0c5123",**
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

In Geth there is no leading 0 in value which exists in Nethermind response.
